      <scopecontent id="aspace_6bdae71ede52ab2acfa95080dd063c3a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains letters to and from David Conner, third party correspondence, and proclamations of the Mexican government, concerning the war between Mexico and the United States, particulary about the Yucatan.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
